    "description": "A lightweight toolset for architects, designers, and fabricators working in Rhino. Ibis covers scale conversion, unit normalization, fabrication tolerances, and batch export \u2014 the small frictions that slow down every design-to-fabrication workflow. Formerly known as Inchworm.",
